        "primer": "The overarching pedagogical goal of this lesson is to help students analyze how the physical, biological, and psychological conditions of the Western Front trenches created entirely new medical challenges that standard 19th-century medical practices could not solve, forcing the RAMC to adapt through organized sanitation, preventive measures, and clinical innovation.",
